    "   - `App\\Repositories\\UserRepository`\n",
    "   - `App\\Repositories\\ProductRepository`\n",
    "\n",
    "2. `index.php`で以下のことを実行\n",
    "   - `use`ステートメントでクラスをインポート\n",
    "   - エイリアスを使って短い名前で参照\n",
    "   - グループ`use`を使って整理\n",
    "\n",
    "**ヒント**:\n",
    - `use App\Services\Database\\Connection as DBConnection;`\n",
